			"editorData": {
				"HowToTrigger": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "Speak to Ogro Niggles - S_GLO_IronThrone_Group1_Prisoner3 c8b6ebf5-e505-4dbd-bd85-dbf82684cbfb - (-58; 37; 68) in the Dock warehouse after saving them.\r\n\r\nQuick setup:\r\n- Load CTY_Main_A\r\n- Use Debug Book (Ctrl + Shift + 9)\r\n- Set Quest Flags and Options -> Act3 (LOW) -> Iron Throne -> Change State -> Back At Docks -> MajoritySaved\r\n- Then talk to the NPC"
				},
